com.camerontec.catalys.util.dictionary

Class MessageInfos

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.util.dictionary.MessageInfos
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMessageInfos

    public class MessageInfos
extends Object
implements IMessageInfos
    Collection (container) of message definitions keyed by the message type (tag). Each definition is in the form of a IMessageInfo

    The IMessageInfo for a given message can be retrieved by message type and by message name.

    The default implementation only specifies required header fields. Required fields for individual message types may optionally be specified.

    Author:
    John Cameron, Cameron Systems Pty Ltd
